{
  "stem": "4760.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we all had still our prisoner clothes on, and then-- you know, the-- they kept us separate, because we came from that same-- transport from Peenemundee, so they kept us in separate barracks.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- I left-- that was in April of '43.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To rebuild a new camp for the V-2.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Camp Dora was a camp-- an underground camp, where in 19-- in the First World War, the German had built tunnels through that mountain.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if it was for train, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were two tunnels, one going-- on both sides there were two big tunnels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they wanted to use this, and there was a big mountain, a mountain where nobody could bomb.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they had try and bombed it, you couldn't penetrate into the-- to-- to the-- to the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in order to manufacture that V-2, they didn't have enough tunnels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we had to dig new tunnels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They only had about two tunnels going across from one side to the other, so they needed about 12 tunnels in order to go in production of the V-2.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had to dynamite the new tunnels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In that way we lost a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of prisoners of war, Russian prisoners who came there from Czechoslovakia-- I mean they were not doing what they're supposed to do with prisoner.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They used the prisoner as workers, not as prisoners, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was always with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother and I stayed all-- we were very fortunate to always stay together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Dora, first were terrible, because we had to sleep in the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one area where they-- where we-- where we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Moist, [INAUDIBLE]-- everything was terrible there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
